title: For Sale:  An honest man just listed .223 rounds!  (hustlers take note)
postcontent:
I wanted to extend my thanks to the gentleman who tonight listed .223 Tullammo rounds at FAIR pricing.  Let those who ask him for his offer take note that it's people like this man-- a generous individual wanting to do some good in this idiotic world-- that we all need to look up to.  I do not know him, but his ACTIONS SPEAK LOUDLY to us all today and let us take this as a sign of things as they really stand... good people are still among us.  

WHAT IF WE ALL followed his move to offer FAIR ammo prices to strangers?  Might just change the world and it's always one person at a time.  Kinda Christ like isn't it???

Whoever you are sir... I commend you and feel your offer to share your wealth with us all, free of profit motive, is PURE GOLD in the lesson it provides us all.  capitalism is not JUST about profit, but sustainability (as in helping other sustain).

Let us all wake up and see the ammo market is a BIG reaction to a non-existent problem and it is our reaction to fear that started all this in the first place.  But while we all are waiting to get a "great deal" let us remember those in need as this man has today.

Much Respect to all who read this and agree-- and especially to this individual who clearly is trying to do some GOOD! We can ALL take a lesson here.
